cess.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The scope of the interior design project plays a significant role in determining the overall timeline. Certain factors, such as client decision-making, supply chain and procurement, construction challenges, and client customisation requests, can cause disruptions or unexpected delays. To streamline the entire process, try to establish clear and regular communication, prioritise decisions, and incorporate buffer time to accommodate unforeseen challenges.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/26163525\/design-timeline-architects-interior-designers-mumbai.jpg\" alt=\"DesignCafe's design timeline process for architecture &amp; interior design in Mumbai, from booking to project production\" class=\"wp-image-61008\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/26163525\/design-timeline-architects-interior-designers-mumbai.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/26163525\/design-timeline-architects-interior-designers-mumbai-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/26163525\/design-timeline-architects-interior-designers-mumbai-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/26163525\/design-timeline-architects-interior-designers-mumbai-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A muted yet sophisticated entertainment space for family and friends<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Personalised home interior designs for cosy vibes at home\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/03182840\/personalised-home-interior-designs-for-cosy-vibes-at-home.jpg \" \/><\/a><